data.description: Welcome to a charming oasis in the heart of the southwest! This delightful smart home boasts an open floor plan with a fully updated kitchen, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a stone backsplash, and an island with a stylish reclaimed wood accent. Recent upgrades include a new water heater, Culligan water softener, and a water purifying system.  The living room showcases a trendy accent wall, adding character to the space. Location is key, and this home is strategically positioned close to the highly rated Forbuss Elementary, making it an ideal choice for families. With all appliances included, this home is ready for you to move in and start creating lasting memories. The home is nestled just 20 minutes from the Strip and the airport, close to Durango Station and The Uncommons.
